WorkItem.ClosedComment: Working as intended, check out Optimizer help page for more information on the subject.
WorkItem.Description: Sometimes when I use the optimizer it generates a gearset with a lower dps. In addition if i get an optimization with a high score and clear my gear or make a new sheet with the same settings i will get a different gearset with lower dps (no 4 piece) such as these

Comments.Message:
Optimization is not guaranteed to always give identical/ideal results. See Thoroughness on the Optimizer dialog.
If you ever have the Optimizer return a result that is lower than your current gearset, that means that you didn't mark everything that you currently have as available. The 'Current Gear/Enchants/Buffs' chart will help easily identify what you missed.
